{
  "stem": "10162.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "From your dresses, to the walls, to the furniture, everything was always redone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She had an idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I guess I must have had pink, and blue, and all these traditional colors.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then I-- well, I remember that suddenly she realized that it would be much nicer to have yellow, or bright yellow with a little red trim.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then she got matching lovely yellow and red flower colored-- flowered curtains that the whole room will look like the sun was always shining in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- I never questioned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just-- I just thought she was-- she did everything wonderfully.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I was very proud of having such a sunny room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "However, I also remember toward the very end she was planning to redo the room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I was getting to be a big girl and I shouldn't have a children's room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was planning to-- to change the bed to something more-- you know, more sophisticated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it-- it never really happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I remember the preparations, the think-- the thoughts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She designed the clothes, and she bought the fabrics, and she also always had some great idea.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, well, like everybody in those days in Hungary-- or almost everybody-- bought the fabric and they had a little dressmaker who would-- who would then sew it up.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was mixed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very friendly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very friendly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a large apartment building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it wasn't very common that-- that Jews and-- and Christians socialized.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "However, almost every Jewish family had a Christian friend and vice versa.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
